revision.text:
{{Italic title}}
'''''Ambergris Today''''' is a weekly newspaper published in [[San Pedro Town]], Ambergris Caye, [[Belize]]. It is a free newspaper, marketed to tourists.<ref name="Goodrich1995">{{cite book|author=Peter Goodrich|title=Oedipus Lex: Psychoanalysis, History, Law|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=XDga7U9bTHsC&pg=PA244|year=1995|publisher=University of California Press|isbn=978-0-520-08990-7|pages=244–}}</ref>

==See also==
*[[List of newspapers in Belize]].

