ekk]], Norwegian journalist *[[1970]] &ndash; [[Steve Avery]], American baseball player * 1970 &ndash; [[Shizuka Kudō]], Japanese singer and actress *[[1971]] &ndash; [[Miguel Calero]], Colombian footballer and manager (d. 2012) * 1971 &ndash; [[Carlos Pérez (pitcher)|Carlos Pérez]], Dominican-American baseball player * 1971 &ndash; [[Gregg Zaun]], American baseball player and sportscaster *[[1972]] &ndash; [[Paul Devlin (footballer)|Paul Devlin]], English-Scottish footballer and manager * 1972 &ndash; [[Roberto Mejía]], Dominican baseball player * 1972 &ndash; [[Dean Potter]], American rock climber and [[BASE jumping|BASE]] jumper (d. 2015) *[[1973]] &ndash; [[Roberto Ayala]], Argentinian footballer * 1973 &ndash; [[Adrien Brody]], American actor * 1973 &ndash; [[Hidetaka Suehiro]], Japanese video game director and writer * 1973 &ndash; [[David Miller (tenor)|David Miller]], American tenor *[[1974]] &ndash; [[Da Brat]], American rapper *[[1975]] &ndash; [[Lita (wrestler)|Lita]], American wrestler * 1975 &ndash; [[Luciano Almeida]], Brazilian footballer * 1975 &ndash; [[Avner Dorman]], Israeli-American composer and academic * 1975 &ndash; [[Konstantinos Nebegleras]], Greek footballer * 1975 &ndash; [[Anderson Silva]], Brazilian mixed martial artist and boxer *[[1976]] &ndash; [[Christian Älvestam]], Swedish singer-songwriter and guitarist * 1976 &ndash; [[Georgina Chapman]], English model, actress, and fashion designer, co-founded [[Marchesa (brand)|Marchesa]] * 1976 &ndash; [[Anna DeForge]], American basketball player * 1976 &ndash; [[Kyle Farnsworth]], American baseball player * 1976 &ndash; [[Nadine Faustin-Parker]], Hatian hurdler<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.iaaf.org/athletes/haiti/nadine-faustin-parker-137016|title=IAAF: Nadine FAUSTIN-PARKER {{!}} Profile|website=iaaf.org|access-date=2018-05-21}}</ref> * 1976 &ndash; [[Jason Wiemer]], Canadian ice hockey player *[[1977]] &ndash; [[Nate Fox]], American basketball player (d. 2014) * 1977 &ndash; [[Martin Kaalma]], Estonian footballer * 1977 &ndash; [[Sarah Michelle Gellar]], American actress and producer * 1977 &ndash; [[Rob McElhenney]], American actor, producer, and screenwriter *[[1978]] &ndash; [[Roland Lessing]], Estonian biathlete *[[1979]] &ndash; [[Iain Balshaw]], English rugby player * 1979 &ndash; [[Rebecca DiPietro]], American wrestler and model * 1979 &ndash; [[Marios Elia]], Cypriot footballer * 1979 &ndash; [[Ross Filipo]], New Zealand rugby player * 1979 &ndash; [[Noé Pamarot]], French footballer * 1979 &ndash; [[Patrick Somerville]], American novelist and short story writer * 1979 &ndash; [[Kerem Tunçeri]], Turkish basketball player *[[1980]] &ndash; [[Win Butler]], American-Canadian singer-songwriter and guitarist * 1980 &ndash; [[Jeremy Smith (rugby league, born 1980)|Jeremy Smith]], New Zealand rugby league player *[[1981]] &ndash; [[Mustafa Güngör]], German rugby player * 1981 &ndash; [[Amy Leach (theatre director)|Amy Leach]], English director and producer *[[1982]] &ndash; [[Uğur Boral]], Turkish footballer * 1982 &ndash; [[Larissa França]], Brazilian volleyball player *[[1983]] &ndash; [[Simona La Mantia]], Italian triple jumper * 1983 &ndash; [[James McFadden]], Scottish footballer * 1983 &ndash; [[William Obeng]], Ghanaian-American football player * 1983 &ndash; [[Nikoloz Tskitishvili]], Georgian basketball player *[[1984]] &ndash; [[Blake Costanzo]], American football player * 1984 &ndash; [[Charles Hamelin]], Canadian speed skater * 1984 &ndash; [[Harumafuji Kōhei]], Mongolian sumo wrestler, the 70th [[Yokozuna]] * 1984 &ndash; [[Adán Sánchez]], American-Mexican musician (d. 2004) * 1984 &ndash; [[Tyler Thigpen]], American football player *[[1985]] &ndash; [[Grant Clitsome]], Canadian ice hockey player *[[1986]] &ndash; [[Matt Derbyshire]], English footballer * 1986 &ndash; [[Goran Gogić]], Serbian footballer (d. 2015) *[[1987]] &ndash; [[Michael Baze]], American jockey (d. 2011) * 1987 &ndash; [[Erwin Hoffer]], Austrian footballer * 1987 &nda