== Scalextric ==
For the 2015 CarFest South, former F1 driver [[Martin Brundle]] created a 45-metre [[Scalextric]] circuit.<ref name="Scalextric">{{cite web|url=http://home.bt.com/lifestyle/motoring/motoring-news/scalextric-track-built-for-chris-evans-carfest-to-be-sold-for-children-in-need-11363997502382|title=Scalextric track built for Chris Evans CarFest to be sold for Children In Need - BT|date=12 August 2015|work=[[BT Group]]|accessdate=12 August 2015}}</ref>
== Air crash ==
During the 2015 event, held at [[Oulton Park]], Cheshire, a [[Folland Gnat]] aircraft, one of pair performing a display, [[Oulton Park Folland Gnat crash|crashed]] into the ground, killing the pilot, Kevin Whyman.<ref name="BBC-33882212">{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-manchester-33882212|title=CarFest pilot death: Aeroplane 'broke into pieces' - BBC News|date=12 August 2015|work=[[BBC Online]]|accessdate=12 August 2015}}</ref>
