{{Use dmy dates|date=October 2015}} {{Infobox music festival |name =Felabration |image =Felaboration promo poster.jpeg |image_size =220px |alt =Photo of Fela with African map on the background |caption =Felabration 2015 promotional poster |genre ={{flatlist| *[[Afrobeat]] *[[Afro pop music|Afropop]] *[[Rhythm and blues|R&B]] *[[Reggae]] *[[Dancehall]]}} |dates = |location =[[New Afrika Shrine]], [[Ikeja]] |years_active =1998&ndash;present |founders =[[Yeni Anikulapo-Kuti]] |attendance = |capacity = |website ={{URL|felabration.net}} }}
'''Felabration''' is an annual music festival conceived in 1998 by [[Yeni Anikulapo-Kuti]] in memory and celebration of her father [[Fela Kuti]], a [[Nigerian]] musician and [[Human rights activists|human rights activist]] known for pioneering the [[afrobeat]] genre of music.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.pmnewsnigeria.com/2015/10/12/sandra-iszadore-fashola-ajibade-others-speak-at-felabration/|title=Sandra Iszadore, Fashola, Ajibade, others speak at Felabration|work=[[P.M. News]]|first=Arogundade|last=Funke|date=12 October 2015|accessdate=15 October 2015}}</ref> The one-week-long event which is held annually at the [[New Afrika Shrine]] in [[Ikeja]], attracts visitors from different countries and has thus been considered as an official tourist destination by the [[Lagos State Government]].<ref>{{cite news|url=http://thenationonlineng.net/as-felabration-2015-kicks-off/|title=AS FELABRATION 2015 KICKS OFF|work=[[The Nation (Nigeria)|The Nation]]|date=12 October 2015|accessdate=15 October 2015}}</ref>
Felabration is held on the week of Fela's birthday. The event features musical performances from top music acts from Nigeria and [[guest appearance]]s from internationally acclaimed musicians and personalities.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://leadership.ng/entertainment/456834/felabration-revs-up-holds-in-october|title=Felabration Revs Up, Holds in October|work=The Leadership|last=Abulude|first=Samuel|date=28 August 2015|accessdate=15 October 2015}}</ref> It also consists of street parades, [[Symposium|symposia]] on social and topical issues, debates and photo exhibitions.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://theeagleonline.com.ng/2015-felabration-to-hold-in-october/|title=2015 Felabration to hold in October|work=The Eagle|last=Akinwale|first=Funsho|date=25 August 2015|accessdate=15 October 2015}}</ref>
