The '''Six Days of Munich''' was a [[Six-day racing|six-day track cycling race]] held annually in [[Munich]], [[Germany]]. The event was first held in 1933 with the last edition held in 2009.<ref>http://www.memoire-du-cyclisme.eu/piste_6jours/6j_munich.php</ref> Starting in 1972, the event was held at the [[Olympiahalle]].

